I just want to point out that some hosts are changing their names
to domain syntax without notifying the NIC so their new official name
can appear in the host table for those hosts not yet converted.

I am getting returned mail when I send to those hosts (i.e.
mit-borax.mit.edu and berkeley.edu (is this a valid host
name? -- Berkeley.edu is also a domain.)

Cheers,
--JSol
Boston University Distributed Systems Group.
